    "summary": "The transcript demonstrates a user asking an AI to improve a \"Clarity Score\" (driven by action verb counts) for an onboarding guide while explicitly warning against keyword stuffing. Across three turns, the model iteratively replaces simple verbs with more \"dynamic\" ones to increase the score, eventually using slightly more sophisticated but still functional vocabulary.",
